  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Nudging supports better decision-making by focusing on related systematic biases.",
    "However, boosting is an intervention to improve cognitive competence for proactive and rational decisionmaking (Hertwig and Grne-Yanoff, 2017).",
    "Shimizu et al. (2022) proposed privacy-aware snippets, which aim to enhance privacy risk judgment in Web searches by providing comprehensive information about sharing conditions of browsing histories.",
    "Harvey et al. (2015) reported that providing examples of high-quality queries can help users learn to improve the efficiency of their query formulation.",
    "Buçinca et al. (2021) reported that the users' final decision-making performance can be improved if they are required to think by themselves before the AIs provide supportive information for decision-making."
  ],
